PN,39901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef was at Manchester Crown Court
OL,9,Ffor the sentencing
OL,11,FTwo men have been jailed after a man
OL,12,Fdied as they drove at more than 100mph
OL,13,Fin what police have called "one of the
OL,14,Fmost extreme dangerous driving cases"
OL,15,Fofficers have ever seen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FUways Hussain and Usmaan Mahmood
OL,8,Ffilmed themselves travelling at more
OL,9,Fthan a 100mph on residential roads in
OL,10,FBurnage, South Manchester, before
OL,11,Fsmashing into Sylvester Abayomi's car
OL,12,Fas he drove to work in March.
OL,14,FThe pair had earlier been seen on CCTV
OL,15,Finhaling nitrous oxide before then
OL,16,Fspending the night racing through the
OL,17,Fstreets and running red lights at more
OL,18,Fthan four-times the speed limit,
OL,19,Freaching 139mph just seconds before
OL,20,Fthe fatal crash.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FDriver Hussain and his passenger
OL,8,FMahmood were then recorded on an apple
OL,9,Fwatch, which had automatically called
OL,10,Femergency services in the moments
OL,11,Fafter the collision, making plans to
OL,12,Fflee the scene and cover up evidence.
OL,14,FBoth have now been jailed for a total
OL,15,Fof more than 24 years after Hussain
OL,16,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,17,Fdriving, while Mahmood admitted aiding
OL,18,Fand abetting the same charge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FIt is believed it is one of the first
OL,8,Ftimes a passenger has been convicted
OL,9,Fof such a charge, and one of the
OL,10,Fhighest for a death by dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving offence involving a single
OL,12,Ffatality.
OL,14,FJailing them, Judge Nicholas Dean KC
OL,15,Fsaid their driving was "deliberate
OL,16,Frisk-taking, seemingly for the thrill
OL,17,Fof it".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,F"It was a sustained, deliberate and
OL,8,Fescalating course of highly dangerous
OL,9,Fconduct over a prolonged period," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"I have seen CCTV images and video
OL,13,Frecordings on phones and they are
OL,14,Fterrifying.
OL,16,F"You drove at extreme speeds,
OL,17,Fseemingly up to very nearly 140mph, on
OL,18,Froads which were by and large subject
OL,19,Fto 30mph speed limits, far, far in
OL,20,Fexcess of any safe or lawful limit."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FManchester Crown Court heard Hussain,
OL,8,F20, and Mahmood, 23, set out in the VW
OL,9,FGolf GTI belonging to Mahmood, which
OL,10,Fneither were insured to drive, at
OL,11,Faround 11pm on 8 March.
OL,13,FAs they stopped for petrol to continue
OL,14,Ftheir racing they were seen on CCTV
OL,15,Finhaling from a balloon filled with
OL,16,FClass C drug Nitrous Oxide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FThe pair then recorded a series of
OL,8,Fvideos on their phones throughout the
OL,9,Fnight showing them weaving in and out
OL,10,Fof traffic, regularly hitting speeds
OL,11,Fof more than 100mph.
OL,13,FBut as they raced down Kingsway the
OL,14,Fpair jumped a red light, smashing into
OL,15,F50-year-old Sylvester Abayomi - known
OL,16,Fas Syll - who worked as a delivery
OL,17,Fdriver, leaving him with fatal
OL,18,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FDespite the crash Hussain and Mahmood
OL,8,Fcontinued driving, reversing down the
OL,9,Froad before parking up, unaware the
OL,10,Fcrash had triggered Hussain's Apple
OL,11,Fwatch and called the emergency
OL,12,Fservices who were recording their
OL,13,Fconversation.
OL,15,FHussain was heard asking Mahmood to
OL,16,F"call an uber" to get them away,
OL,17,Fbefore the pair discussed if Syll was
OL,18,Fdead and making a plan to tell police
OL,19,Fthe car had been stolen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FJudge Dean described the transcript of
OL,8,Fthe call as "chilling", adding: "It
OL,9,Fdoesn't reveal shock or concern for
OL,10,Fthe victim."
OL,12,FCCTV from a nearby shop also showed
OL,13,Fthe duo removing nitrous oxide
OL,14,Fcanisters from the back of the car.
OL,16,FThe pair, who were still being tracked
OL,17,Fby their Apple watch, were arrested
OL,18,Fshortly afterwards after fleeing the
OL,19,Fscene.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@VO]pD@aOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FPaying tribute, Sylvester's partner,
OL,8,FDenise, said: "On Monday 9 March, the
OL,9,Flove of my life was taken away, he was
OL,10,Fthe most caring soul and gentle person
OL,11,Fyou could ever meet.
OL,13,F"He had time for everybody and was
OL,14,Floved by everyone. Syll will be sadly
OL,15,Fmissed."
OL,26,@pD@OOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FAddressing the defendants she told the
OL,8,Fcourt: "Sylvester was simply on his
OL,9,Fway to work. An ordinary hard-working
OL,10,Fman. He should have returned home to
OL,11,Fme safely that day. Because of your
OL,12,Factions he never did.
OL,14,F"You left Sylv to die alone. You did
OL,15,Fnot show him even a shred of
OL,16,Fcompassion or humanity."
OL,26,@pD@HOUvD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FHussain of Marley Road, Manchester,
OL,8,Fwho had indicated a guilty plea at
OL,9,Fmagistrates court, was sentenced to 11
OL,10,Fyears and eight months detention after
OL,11,Fadmitting causing death by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving, causing death by driving
OL,13,Fwhilst uninsured, and failing to
OL,14,Fprovide a specimen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
