OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780229466
OL,3,CMen jailed after man dies in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe most extreme dangerous driving
OL,5,Ccases'
OL,7,FMahmood of Buller Road, Manchester,
OL,8,Fwho initially told police he tried to
OL,9,Fwarn Hussain about his driving before
OL,10,Fpleading guilty, was jailed for 12
OL,11,Fyears and nine months for aiding and
OL,12,Fabetting causing death by dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving and aiding and abetting
OL,14,Fcausing death by driving whilst
OL,15,Funinsured.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
